## Checklist — Adding a page

- [ ] New page has correct nav (same as all others + own link as `active`)
- [ ] home.html card added in sequence order with step-badge and level-pill
- [ ] roadmap.html sequence **table** row added (correct phase header)
- [ ] roadmap.html **VP_PHASES** step added (same `n`, `label`, `href` as table); all steps renumbered; intro «N шагов» updated
- [ ] roadmap.html **NODES** array entry added (with correct rank/level/cat/desc)
- [ ] roadmap.html **EDGES** wired (prerequisites → new node → dependents)
- [ ] `rg` self-check: new `href` present in roadmap table + `VP_PHASES` + home (if topicCard)
- [ ] Mental model `.mm-row` added if new concept layer
- [ ] app.js PAGES array updated
- [ ] All existing pages have nav link to new page

## Checklist — Removing a page

- [ ] Nav link removed from all `.html` files
- [ ] home.html card removed, step-badges renumbered
- [ ] roadmap.html table row removed
- [ ] roadmap.html VP_PHASES step removed; steps renumbered
- [ ] roadmap.html NODES entry removed
- [ ] roadmap.html EDGES referencing removed node cleaned up
- [ ] Mental model row removed if layer gone
- [ ] app.js PAGES entry removed
